{"id":"synth-data-1l0.23","title":"Scoring system: rubrics.yaml, auto_grader.py, scoring_template.xlsx","description":"Per-test-case 5-dimension rubric (Correctness/Completeness/Format/Robustness/Communication, 1-3 scale). Pass ≥2.4 avg, Conditional ≥2.0 + no 1s, Fail \u003c2.0 or any 1.\n\nDeliverables:\n- rubrics.yaml — scoring criteria per TC\n- auto_grader.py — validates numerical outputs vs gold, checks canaries, detects planted errors, outputs JSON per TC + aggregate\n- scoring_template.xlsx — 4 sheets:\n  1. Scorecard (1 row per TC, 5 dimension columns + notes)\n  2. Grader Instructions (per-dimension, per-TC guidance)\n  3. Inter-Rater Agreement (2 raters' scores + Cohen's kappa computation)\n  4. Aggregate Dashboard — capability matrix pivots on 3 axes:\n     Axis 1: Service Line (Audit, Tax, Advisory, Cross-Service)\n     Axis 2: Capability (File Reading, File Writing, Data Analysis/SQL/DataFrame, RAG, Multi-Step Workflow)\n     Axis 3: Difficulty (Routine, Complex, Adversarial)\n     Each TC maps to ≥1 cell. Dashboard shows pass rates by each combination.\n\nSee prompt.md §7.1-§7.5.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","owner":"platon2001@icloud.com","created_at":"2026-04-08T13:33:24Z","created_by":"platon2001","updated_at":"2026-04-08T14:08:25Z","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"synth-data-1l0.23","depends_on_id":"synth-data-1l0","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-08T15:33:24Z","created_by":"platon2001","metadata":"{}"},{"issue_id":"synth-data-1l0.23","depends_on_id":"synth-data-1l0.24","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-08T15:34:09Z","created_by":"platon2001","metadata":"{}"}],"dependency_count":1,"dependent_count":1,"comment_count":0}
